{"tid":2213642,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) 點解同一個file airdrop 同 iPhoto 會咁唔同？","createTime":"2020-09-22T16:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T11:23:14.000Z","uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f462a8a82fad9020ef39cbbbf403fe5099232c72","tid":2213642,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"最近想backup手機 發現同一個file<br />\n如果係電腦iPhoto 就咁down同airdrop會好大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（如圖，左係airdrop 右係iCloud）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJ1F7zU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJ1F7zU.png&h=7f6ae24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我冇set到optimise storage所以理論上應該係同一條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAirDrop的話冇set most compatible 就會好似圖左咁成百幾mb 有就大iPhoto少少46.6mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以觀察到嘅分別就係iPhoto down落嚟啲話好似create咗個新file冇咗啲metadata<br />\n但係Dimension, Codec啲setting應該都一樣 畫質好似都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲知點解會咁大分別？<br />\n點樣過大量片落電腦最好？我唔特別需要啲metadata，個create date and time 同畫質一樣就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef5c4a692784e10ce10fd6c6d7b02fe704ec244","tid":2213642,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T19:09:53.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fb9035dbade8999006df3c2600a8cb721c8510","tid":2213642,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ef5c4a692784e10ce10fd6c6d7b02fe704ec244","tid":2213642,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T19:09:53.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply